OL,6,FWholesale energy prices have also
OL,7,Fdropped in recent weeks, which is set
OL,8,Fto keep a lid on price hikes from
OL,9,FApril, Cornwall Insight said.
OL,11,FRegulator Ofgem said Thursday's
OL,12,Fincrease to the cap, which was
OL,13,Fannounced in November, was being
OL,14,Fdriven by the funding of nuclear power
OL,15,Fprojects and discounts to some
OL,16,Fhouseholds' winter bills.
