OL,6,FNed Hammond, the deputy director of
OL,7,FEnergy UK, which represents suppliers,
OL,8,Fsaid: "While the new price cap coming
OL,9,Finto force only includes a small rise,
OL,10,Fit still means energy bills are too
OL,11,Fhigh for too many households. Gas
OL,12,Fprices may have declined in recent
OL,13,Fmonths but remain higher than previous
OL,14,Fyears, while increasing policy costs
OL,15,Fare also adding to bills.
