OL,6,F"Meanwhile, the wider energy industry
OL,7,Fhas made more than #125 billion in UK
OL,8,Fprofits since 2020, including firms
OL,9,Foperating in a dying North Sea. This
OL,10,Fisn't a crisis of scarcity, it's a
OL,11,Fcrisis of priorities. Ministers must
OL,12,Fmove beyond short-term price cap
OL,13,Ftweaks and get serious about ending
OL,14,Ffuel poverty by investing in energy
OL,15,Fefficiency, reforming energy pricing,
OL,16,Fintroducing a fair social tariff and
OL,17,Ffully funding the Warm Homes Plan."
