OL,6,F"If you're on a variable tariff, make
OL,7,Fsure to submit a meter reading to
OL,8,Fensure you pay the cheaper rates for
OL,9,Fany energy used before the new price
OL,10,Fcap takes effect."
OL,12,FDr Craig Lowrey, principal consultant
OL,13,Fat Cornwall Insight, said: "Households
OL,14,Fwill welcome a cut in April, bringing
OL,15,Fthe cap to its lowest level since
OL,16,F2024. That's a step towards the
OL,17,FGovernment's #300 reduction target by
OL,18,F2030 and will ease some pressure on
OL,19,Fboth families and policymakers.
